data.name: ALGINATE DRESSINGS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Calcium Alginate and carboxylmethylcellulose (CMC) fabric

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Various Shapes

## PERFORMANCE
- Skin friendly
- Hypoallergenic
- Hemostatic Effect
- Non-Adhesive
- Highly Absorbent
